# Hexagonal Architecture

## Layers

- **Domain** (`src/Domain/`): Pura. Sin dependencias de frameworks. Entidades, Value Objects, Excepciones, interfaces de Repositorios, Eventos.
- **Application** (`src/Application/`): Casos de uso (UseCase/), DTOs, Ports (interfaces), Services. Depende solo de Domain.
- **Infrastructure** (`src/Infrastructure/`): Implementaciones técnicas — Doctrine, Controllers Symfony, Voters, ApiClients, UI React.

## Dependency Rule

Domain nunca importa Infrastructure ni Application.
Application nunca importa Infrastructure.
Los Controllers son delgados: reciben request → llaman UseCase → devuelven respuesta.

## Backend folder structure

```
src/
├── Domain/
│   ├── Entity/         # Aggregates
│   ├── Repository/     # Interfaces (puertos)
│   ├── ValueObject/
│   └── Exception/
├── Application/
│   ├── UseCase/        # Commands / Queries
│   ├── DTO/
│   ├── Port/           # Interfaces para infra
│   └── Service/
└── Infrastructure/
    ├── Symfony/
    │   ├── Controller/
    │   ├── Voter/
    │   └── Validator/
    ├── Persistence/Doctrine/
    │   ├── Entity/     # Mapeo DB
    │   └── Repository/ # Implementaciones
    └── ApiClient/
```
